    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Years of Alaska\nSpirit\nMake Milies\nGood Morning,\nand welcome aboard Alaska Airlines!\nWe hope that you will enjoy our\nmeal service while flying with us to\nBoston, Massachusetts",
      "To start our breakfast service\nWarmed Breakfast Pastry and Fresh Fruit Plate\nA Choice of Entrées\nOmelette with Mushroom Chardonnay Cream Sauce\nGrilled Seasoned Chicken Sausage, Roesti Potatoes\nCheese Blintz with Raspberry Sauce,\nGrilled Country Ham, Scrambled Eggs w/ Chives\nWe Proudly Feature\nSeattle's Best Coffee.\nBon appetit!"
    ],
